  "tacticalAnalysis": {
    "TUR": {
      "summary": "Turkey dominated every possession metric in 4-2-3-1 but fell to painful 0-1 defeat. With 80.8% possession and 153 completed line breaks, Crescent-Stars created volume without reward — only 5 of 32 attempts hit target and 2.13 xG was drastically underperformed.",
