        "50 forced turnovers and 367 defensive pressures — highest pressure count of matchday"
      ],
      "weaknesses": [
        "19.2% possession and 54% pass accuracy — complete concession of ball to Turkey",
        "Only 0.36 xG from 7 attempts; win built almost entirely on defensive solidity",
        "3 defensive line breaks conceded risked exposing limited backline",
        "Tactical plan entirely dependent on holding single early lead for 88 minutes"
      ]
